name: Yětù
description:
You are a magic rabbit trying to save your planet from dying. 

Root the trees to the center of the planet to bring new life into the cold rock of your home! 

Use the A- and D-keys to move the rabbit left or right and to let the roots grow into the desired destination.

This is a submission to the Global Game Jam 2023.
